Reduction Trigger Mutiplexer Outputs
TrigMux (Trigger Multiplexer) » Enumerated Types » Reduction Trigger Mutiplexers

General Description

Enumerations

enum  en_trig_output_grp9_t
 For PERI_ver1: the enumerated type that represents a trigger reduction multiplexer group #9 output signals, used by Cy_TrigMux_Connect and Cy_TrigMux_SwTrigger functions. Refer to a family-specific device header file, e.g. <PDL_DIR>/devices/include/psoc6_01_config.h.
